				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-5-T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-gi%C3%A1m-Giang-H%E1%BA%A1-L%C3%BD-c%C3%B4ng-Ung/poem-Qu1ia6IYu7v8HffB5dNOyA">Bát ai thi kỳ 5 - Tặng bí thư giám Giang Hạ Lý công Ung - 八哀詩其五－贈秘書監江夏李公邕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%C3%A1p-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-h%C3%A0n-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-h%E1%BB%AFu-ho%C3%A0i/poem-H_0WU3qat1dL6zjVciaajA">Đáp Vương thập nhị hàn dạ độc chước hữu hoài - 答王十二寒夜獨酌有懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-T%E1%BA%A7n-k%E1%BB%B7/poem-eiofWwgK57JEwWhQBX1Iyw">Độc “Tần kỷ” - 讀秦紀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/author-8wX_f--qBGvseLM4iD_Z7A">Trần Cung Doãn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%E1%BA%A3o-li%E1%BB%85u-ca-ch%C3%BA/poem-6HMc4oIz_l7i-7ZKwrHtVg">Hảo liễu ca chú - 好了歌注</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%E1%BB%B1u-ph%C3%B3-s%C3%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-chi-nh%E1%BA%A5t/poem-WcERQdT6ZO_dgjdg6b-3ow">Hựu phó sách đề vịnh chi nhất - 又副冊題詠之一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-B%C3%A2n/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-t%C3%A1i-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-pe0NCHff79hoK4zhNqZrLg">Nhập tái khúc kỳ 1 - 入塞曲其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1